                {"swissGerman": "Werktäg", "german": "Werktage", "explanation": "'Werktäg' = 'Werktage'. Business days."},
                {"swissGerman": "Briefmarke", "german": "Briefmarken", "explanation": "Same: stamps. Swiss Post also uses 'A-Post' and 'B-Post' categories."},
